{"conceptual":"\n<p sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"8\" sourceendlinenumber=\"8\">As of version 3.9.0 all future indexes use 64-bit hashes instead of 32-bit hashes. Event Store automatically transitions your indexes from 32-bit to 64-bit by writing all new indexes as 64-bit indexes during the merge process.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"10\" sourceendlinenumber=\"10\">If you prefer to use only 64-bit indexes immediately you can force this change. For a small database, delete the <em>index</em> folder in your database folder, and let it rebuild (this might take a while)</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"12\" sourceendlinenumber=\"12\">If you have a large database, or it&#39;s stored in remote storage, and you can&#39;t lose downtime, you can run this operation offline on another node with the following steps:</p>\n<ol sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"14\" sourceendlinenumber=\"20\">\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"14\" sourceendlinenumber=\"14\"><a href=\"~/server/database-backup.md\" data-raw-source=\"[Take a back up](~/server/database-backup.md)\" sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"14\" sourceendlinenumber=\"14\">Take a back up</a>.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\" sourceendlinenumber=\"15\"><a href=\"~/server/database-backup.md\" data-raw-source=\"[Restore the backup](~/server/database-backup.md)\" sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\" sourceendlinenumber=\"15\">Restore the backup</a> to fast local disks.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"16\" sourceendlinenumber=\"16\">Delete the <em>index</em> folder from back up.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"17\" sourceendlinenumber=\"17\">Run Event Store with a cluster size 3 to prevent other writes. It will rebuild the index.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"18\" sourceendlinenumber=\"18\">Restore the index back to a node (<em>index</em> folder).</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"19\" sourceendlinenumber=\"19\">Let Event Store catch up from master.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"20\" sourceendlinenumber=\"20\">Repeat the restore for other nodes.</li>\n</ol>\n<p sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"22\" sourceendlinenumber=\"22\">For other indices, your index will change to 64-bit due to the merging process that occurs over time.</p>\n","type":"Conceptual","source":{"remote":{"path":"server/64-bit-index.md","branch":"feature/stats-REST","repo":"git@github.com:EventStore/docs.geteventstore.com.git"},"startLine":0.0,"endLine":0.0,"isExternal":false},"path":"server/64-bit-index.md","documentation":{"remote":{"path":"server/64-bit-index.md","branch":"feature/stats-REST","repo":"git@github.com:EventStore/docs.geteventstore.com.git"},"startLine":0.0,"endLine":0.0,"isExternal":false},"_docfxVersion":"2.43.3.0","_disableBreadcrumb":true,"_enableSearch":true,"_gitContribute":{"branch":"master"},"_appFaviconPath":"assets/favicon.ico","_appTitle":"Event Store","_appFooter":"&copy; 2019 Event Store Limited","_disableNavbar":false,"_disableToc":true,"_systemKeys":["conceptual","type","source","path","documentation","title","rawTitle","wordCount"],"title":"Rebuilding Indexes","rawTitle":"<h1 id=\"rebuilding-indexes\" sourcefile=\"server/64-bit-index.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"6\" sourceendlinenumber=\"6\">Rebuilding Indexes</h1>","outputFileName":"index.html","sinceVersion":"3.9.0","wordCount":176.0,"_lang":"csharp","_tocPath":"toc.html","_navPath":"toc.html","_rel":"../../","_path":"server/64-bit-index/index.html","_key":"server/64-bit-index.md","_navRel":"../../toc.html","_tocRel":"../../toc.html","_navKey":"~/to